data.characterDescription:
**Ethnicity:** Northern European, likely Scandinavian or Germanic descent

**Age:** 25-30 years

**Build:** Slender frame, narrow shoulders, graceful neck with visible collarbone definition

**Skin:** Fair complexion with warm peachy-pink undertones, smooth texture, minimal visible pores, slight natural flush on cheeks, even tone throughout face and décolletage

**Hair:** Platinum blonde to light golden blonde, fine texture, short pixie-length cut swept back from face, slightly longer on top (2-3 inches), tapered shorter at sides and nape, natural wave pattern, appears soft and wispy

**Eyes:** Large, almond-shaped with slight downward tilt at outer corners, striking blue-gray iris with darker limbal ring, clear whites, long natural lashes with medium density, moderate lid space visible, slightly deep-set

**Eyebrows:** Natural arched shape, medium thickness, tapered at tails, light blonde color matching hair, well-groomed but not overly shaped, sparse inner corners

**Face shape:** Oval to heart-shaped, high prominent cheekbones, defined jawline tapering to slightly pointed chin, balanced proportions, moderate forehead height

**Nose:** Straight bridge with very subtle bump at mid-point, medium width, refined tip with slight upturn, narrow nostrils, proportionate to face

**Lips:** Medium fullness, natural pink tone, defined cupid's bow on upper lip, slightly fuller lower lip, balanced width, smooth texture

**Distinguishing marks:** Light natural freckling across nose bridge and upper cheeks (subtle), slight asymmetry with left eye appearing marginally smaller, natural beauty mark possibilities minimal, clean skin without visible scarring, ears medium-sized with attached lobes visible in profile views

**Facial expressions range:** Neutral resting face shows composed, serene quality; smile reveals straight teeth, creates crow's feet at eye corners, lifts cheekbones prominently; full smile is broad and genuine with visible upper teeth
